    <h3>Hints and emails</h3>

    <p>We received and responded to <b>3,409</b> hints from kickoff to wrapup, with requests roughly following a regular pattern, increasing as teams unlocked more puzzles.</p>

    <div class="flourish-embed flourish-chart" data-src="visualisation/8483180"><script src="https://public.flourish.studio/resources/embed.js"></script></div>

    <p>We also observed a spike of requests occurring in the time leading up to ”HQ close“ at 6pm on Sunday.</p>

    <div class="flourish-embed flourish-chart" data-src="visualisation/8483033"><script src="https://public.flourish.studio/resources/embed.js"></script></div>

    <div class="flourish-embed flourish-chart" data-src="visualisation/8483336"><script src="https://public.flourish.studio/resources/embed.js"></script></div>

    <p>Emails were in line with overall hint volume throughout the event, with us  receiving 1,487 emails and sending 743 (non-automated) emails, with a large number of emails from teams regarding  administrative issues in the opening hours of the Hunt. We also sent 3,713 automated emails.</p>

    <div class="flourish-embed flourish-chart" data-src="visualisation/8492478"><script src="https://public.flourish.studio/resources/embed.js"></script></div>
    <p>The Investigation generated remarkably few hints, amounting to approximately one hint for every ten teams that unlocked it.</p>

